title: Software Services Agreement
summary: ERP Development, Support and Maintenance Services
meta: | type: contract | ref: SSA-2026-001 | theme: legal | date: 2026-06-24

section: 1. Definitions

def: Services | meaning: Software development, implementation, support and maintenance activities described in this agreement

def: Deliverables | meaning: Source code, documentation, configurations, reports and related outputs produced under the services

def: Confidential Information | meaning: Non-public business, technical or financial information disclosed by either party

def: Business Day | meaning: Any day excluding Fridays, Saturdays and official public holidays in Qatar

section: 2. Parties

contact: UTS Technologies W.L.L. | role: Provider | email: [contracts@uts.qa](mailto:contracts@uts.qa) | country: QA

contact: Client Organization | role: Client | email: [procurement@example.com](mailto:procurement@example.com) | country: QA

section: 3. Scope of Services

text: The Provider shall design, develop, configure, deploy and support software systems requested by the Client.

obligation: Deliver agreed project milestones | owner: Provider

obligation: Provide access to required stakeholders and information | owner: Client

deliverable: ERP platform implementation | phase: delivery

deliverable: Technical documentation | phase: handover

deliverable: User training sessions | phase: onboarding

section: 4. Commercial Terms

metric: Contract Value | value: 250000 | unit: QAR

payment: Advance payment | percentage: 30

payment: Delivery payment | percentage: 40

payment: Acceptance payment | percentage: 30

deadline: Final payment due | date: 2026-12-31 | consequence: Service suspension may apply

section: 5. Project Governance

milestone: Project Kickoff | date: 2026-07-01

milestone: Prototype Delivery | date: 2026-08-15

milestone: User Acceptance Testing | date: 2026-10-15

milestone: Production Go-Live | date: 2026-11-01

risk: Delayed stakeholder feedback | severity: medium | mitigation: Weekly review meetings

risk: Scope expansion | severity: high | mitigation: Formal change request process

section: 6. Service Level Agreement

sla: Critical Incident Response | target: 1 hour | priority: P1

sla: High Incident Response | target: 4 hours | priority: P2

sla: Normal Incident Response | target: 1 business day | priority: P3

warranty: Defect correction period | period: 90 days

section: 7. Intellectual Property

clause: Ownership of Deliverables | owner: Client

text: Upon full payment, ownership of project-specific deliverables transfers to the Client.

clause: Pre-Existing Materials | owner: Provider

text: The Provider retains ownership of frameworks, libraries, tools and reusable intellectual property developed independently of this agreement.

section: 8. Confidentiality

obligation: Protect confidential information | owner: Both Parties

obligation: Restrict disclosure to authorized personnel | owner: Both Parties

deadline: Confidentiality survival period | date: 2031-06-24

section: 9. Warranties

warranty: Professional services warranty | owner: Provider | period: Agreement term

text: Services will be performed using reasonable skill, care and industry standards.

section: 10. Limitation of Liability

clause: Liability Cap | cap: 12 months fees

clause: Excluded Damages | excludes: indirect consequential punitive damages

section: 11. Governing Law

text: This agreement shall be governed by the laws of the State of Qatar.

jurisdiction: Courts of Qatar

section: 12. Approval Workflow

route: sequential

require: legal

require: finance

require: executive

