approve: Financial review completed | by: Khalid Hassan | role: finance | at: 2026-06-24

approve: Executive authorization | by: Ahmed Al-Thani | role: executive | at: 2026-06-24

section: 13. Execution

approve: Executed for Provider | by: Authorized Representative | role: provider | at: 2026-06-24

approve: Executed for Client | by: Authorized Representative | role: client | at: 2026-06-24

